PART 8 — DAMAGE FORMULA (LOCKED)
Final Damage Formula
```
Final Damage = Base CL × (1 + Additive%) × Multipliers → Soft Cap
```
Step 1 — Additive Bucket (adds together, not multiplied)
Source	Bonus
Cook depth 2 ingredients	+5%
Cook depth 3 ingredients	+10%
Cook depth 4+ ingredients	+15%
Step 2 — Multipliers (multiply together)
Source	Multiplier
Allergy match	×1.75
Non-allergen	×0.75
Craving State	×1.5 (consumed on hit)
Mark bonus	×1.15–1.20
Step 3 — Soft Cap (anti-break safety net)
Raw multiplier	Actual output
≤ 3.0×	Full value
3.0–4.0×	80% efficiency
4.0×+	65% efficiency
Worked Example — Full Stack
Craving active, 4-ingredient Rare dish (Mapo Tofu, CL 38), allergic target:
38 × 1.15 (cook depth) = 43.7
Raw multiplier: 1.75 (allergy) × 1.5 (craving) = 2.625×
2.625× is in ≤3.0× band → full value
Final: 43.7 × 2.625 = ~115 CL
> This requires: perfect allergy match, active Craving, 4-ingredient cook. High skill, high payoff. The soft cap kicks in when Mark is also stacked on top.
