PART 20 — SERVER ARCHITECTURE (LOCKED TARGET)
Core Principles
Server owns all state. Client sends actions, never results.
EventBus prevents spaghetti — systems fire events, other systems listen. No direct cross-system calls.
UpdateClientState sends only changed values per tick — not full dumps.
Never trust client for: damage dealt, inventory contents, cooking completion, hit position.
Always validate server-side: distance checks, ownership, recipe legality, weight limits.
Folder Structure
```
ReplicatedStorage
 ├── Remotes
 │   ├── RequestPickup
 │   ├── RequestThrow
 │   ├── RequestCookStart
 │   ├── RequestCookFinish
 │   ├── RequestCheckout
 │   ├── RequestBathroomUse
 │   ├── RequestAllianceOffer
 │   └── UpdateClientState
 └── Shared
     ├── IngredientData    ← single source of truth for all ingredient stats
     ├── RecipeData        ← single source of truth for all recipe stats
     └── Constants         ← all locked tuning values

ServerScriptService
 ├── Core
 │   ├── PlayerState       ← all per-player state (CL, FL, inventory, alliance, marks, craving)
 │   ├── DataManager       ← DataStore + session state
 │   └── EventBus          ← central pub/sub
 ├── Systems
 │   ├── BarSystem         ← CL + FL tracking, thresholds, 100% state, debuffs
 │   ├── InventorySystem   ← pickup, drop, weight, capacity, pickup speed scaling
 │   ├── CookingSystem     ← recipe validation, timers, burn, sous-chef, deconstruct
 │   ├── CombatSystem      ← throw validation, hit detection, damage formula, soft cap
 │   ├── ComboSystem       ← marks, craving state, elemental chains, CC + diminishing returns
 │   ├── BathroomSystem    ← Potty Break tracking, sink/toilet, elimination
 │   ├── AllianceSystem    ← bracelet formation, reconfirmation, end-game vote
 │   ├── EconomySystem     ← budget, checkout (self + staffed), scan timing, queue
 │   └── PointsSystem      ← scoring, skill modifiers, risk modifiers, accolades
 └── Managers
     ├── MatchManager      ← phase transitions and timers
     ├── SpawnManager      ← ingredient + loot spawn, Legendary placement
     └── CombatManager     ← projectile lifecycle, pooling, AoE zones

StarterPlayerScripts
 └── ClientControllers
     ├── InputController   ← throw charge, interact, scan click inputs
     ├── UIController      ← all HUD updates from server state
     └── VFXController     ← splats, effects, status indicators, 100% cue
