The deli counter (Z=100, store-facing side) is a mid-tier loot node that players can access from the store floor without entering the Kitchen zone.
Design rules:
Ingredients spawn on the deli counter surface facing Z<100 (store side)
Players standing at Z<100 can pick up deli counter items without triggering Kitchen zone logic
